{
  "chapter": 3,
  "chapter_summary": "第三回 怜香惜玉的花如玉\n\n花如玉如花似玉地走进乱石山，表面怜香惜玉地为风四娘收尸，实则心机深沉。金菩萨、人上人、厉青锋三人各怀鬼胎，却不敢与花如玉为敌。\n\n风四娘在心心的照料下苏醒，得知自己被花如玉设计\"毒死\"以摆脱争夺。心心展现高超的用毒和易容技巧，原来之前中毒只是演戏。\n\n花如玉现身，与风四娘展开一场精彩的心理博弈。他自称是风四娘的丈夫，声称端午节成亲，让风四娘百口莫辩。花如玉的武功深不可测，谈吐间尽显城府。\n\n在洞房中，风四娘试图反抗却被花如玉轻松制服。花如玉展现出惊人的武功和酒量，风四娘的计谋一一被识破。两人在心理和武力上展开激烈较量，最终风四娘被迫面对这个如花似玉却心如蛇蝎的男人。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "花如玉！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你照顾她？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你几时变成这么好心的？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我本就是个怜香惜玉的人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "听你说得这么好听，她难道不是死在你手上的？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "金菩萨菩萨心肠，是不是肯替她料理后事？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "厉青锋人称侠盗，难道也不肯？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "也许他想换换口味，吃个死人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你的手……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我的手没有风四娘美。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你还有两只手？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_xin",
      "speaker_name": "心心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我一直都有两只手。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我还以为你有三只手哩。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_xin",
      "speaker_name": "心心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "怎么会有三只手？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "若没有三只手，刚才中了毒的那只手怎么不见了？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那只不过是一点点毒？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_xin",
      "speaker_name": "心心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "很少的一点点。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可是你刚才……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_xin",
      "speaker_name": "心心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_xin",
      "speaker_name": "心心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我怎么会到这里来的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_xin",
      "speaker_name": "心心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是我们抬你来的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "抬我来的？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_xin",
      "speaker_name": "心心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你刚才已死过一次。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_xin",
      "speaker_name": "心心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我怎么死的？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_xin",
      "speaker_name": "心心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我送去的那套衣服上有毒。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "连衣服上都能下毒？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_xin",
      "speaker_name": "心心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "别人不能，花公子能。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他为什么要毒死我？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为他怕别人把你撕成好几半。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "刚才来抢我的人实在不少。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_xin",
      "speaker_name": "心心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可是你一死，那些人就全都连沾都不敢沾你了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所以你们就把我抬了回来？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "无论你是死是活，我们都一样会照顾你的。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们连死人都能救得活？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_xin",
      "speaker_name": "心心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "别人不能，花公子能。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "看来你们这位花公子，真是个了不起的人。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_xin",
      "speaker_name": "心心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为什么不让我看看他？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_xin",
      "speaker_name": "心心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "就算我想不让你看他，他也不答应的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_xin",
      "speaker_name": "心心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "今天的菜是我准备的，有肥鸡烧鸭子、云片豆腐一品、燕窝火熏鸡丝、攒丝锅烧鸡一品、肥鸡火熏炖白菜一品、三鲜丸子一品、鹿筋炖肉一品、清蒸鸭子糊猪肉一品、炒鸡一品、燕窝鸭条、鲜虾丸子、脍鸭腰、溜海参各一品、外加鸡泥萝卜酱、肉丝炒翅子、酱鸭子、咸菜炒茭白、四碟下酒菜，还有野鸡汤一品、酥油茄子一品、粳米膳一品、竹节卷小头一品、蜂糕一品……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_xin",
      "speaker_name": "心心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你还不知道够不够吃？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_xin",
      "speaker_name": "心心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你以为我是谁？是个大肚子的弥勒佛？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我只不过知道你一定饿得很。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_xin",
      "speaker_name": "心心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "想不到花公子居然还是风四娘的知己。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "能有四娘这样的红粉知己，花如玉死而无憾。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "看来又是心心多嘴。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但她却还没有告诉我，这里究竟是什么地方？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "四娘本是到什么地方来的？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "乱石山。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这里就是乱石山。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "乱石山有这么漂亮的地方？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我只不过从不愿虐待自己而已。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "看来你不但是我的知己，还是我的同道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你不是他们的同道？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你不像，但他们都是想谋谁的财，害谁的命呢？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "萧十一郎，当然是萧十一郎。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你是不是为了萧十一郎来的？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "真的不是？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是什么打动了你？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是一个人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只可惜这次我说的不是谎话。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "除了四娘外，世上还有什么人能要我到这种地方来？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我好像并没有要你到这种地方来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只可惜我还是非来不可。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "非来不可？为什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "原来花大哥是为了花大嫂而来的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所以你最好还是小心点。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小心什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她不会。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "难道这位花大嫂从来也不吃醋？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她常常吃醋，但是却绝不会吃你的醋。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为花大嫂就是你，你也就是花大嫂。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "原来我就是花大嫂。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你本来就是的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我是什么时候嫁给你的呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你自己难道忘了？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我忘了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "其实你不该忘记的，因为那天正好是五月初五。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "端午节？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，我们就是端午节那天成的亲。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但现在我既然又找到了你，就绝不会再让你溜了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 362
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我知道。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "洞房我已经又再准备好了。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 378
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这么好的菜，不吃岂非可惜？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "怎么会笑不出？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 396
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你不怕我把你吃穷？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 398
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "能娶到你这么有福气的老婆，我怎么会穷？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 400,
      "line_end": 400
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你吃完了？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 406
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "今天我胃口不好，少吃一点。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 408,
      "line_end": 408
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那么现在……",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 410,
      "line_end": 410
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我当然陪你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 416,
      "line_end": 416
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我喝多少，你就喝多少？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 418,
      "line_end": 418
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "别人不来灌我，新娘子难道反而想灌醉我？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 420,
      "line_end": 420
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "喝酒的人，谁没有喝醉过？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 442,
      "line_end": 442
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所以你也喝醉过？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 444,
      "line_end": 444
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我常醉。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 446,
      "line_end": 446
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可是你喝起来并不像常会喝醉的样子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 448,
      "line_end": 448
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁说的，去年我就醉过一次。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 450,
      "line_end": 450
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "去年？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 452,
      "line_end": 452
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "五年前我也醉过一次",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 454,
      "line_end": 454
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你这一辈子只醉过两次？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 456,
      "line_end": 456
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "两次已经很多了，",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 458,
      "line_end": 458
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有些人一天醉两次，也不嫌多。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 460,
      "line_end": 460
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "其实我也想多醉几次，只可惜酒总是不够。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 462,
      "line_end": 462
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "要多少酒才够？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 464,
      "line_end": 464
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你还想喝多少？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 480,
      "line_end": 480
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一点也不喝了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 482,
      "line_end": 482
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那么现在……",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 484,
      "line_end": 484
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在我们就进洞房去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 486,
      "line_end": 486
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "唱得好，新娘子有赏。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 506,
      "line_end": 506
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "赏什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 508,
      "line_end": 508
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "赏你一个大耳光。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 510,
      "line_end": 510
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "其实你用不着赶她走她也会走的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 514,
      "line_end": 514
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁说我用不着赶她走？我已经急死了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 516,
      "line_end": 516
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "急什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 518,
      "line_end": 518
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你猜呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 520,
      "line_end": 520
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "二十一。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 526,
      "line_end": 526
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你呢？你懂不懂风情？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 540,
      "line_end": 540
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你很快就会知道的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 542,
      "line_end": 542
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小弟弟，你是我的小弟弟，姐姐喜欢你……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 548,
      "line_end": 548
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你喜欢我什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 550,
      "line_end": 550
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我喜欢你去死。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 552,
      "line_end": 552
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 586,
      "line_end": 586
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你……你想怎么样？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 588,
      "line_end": 588
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你猜呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 590,
      "line_end": 590
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他轻轻叹了口气，又道：",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 596,
      "line_end": 596
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我应该等到什么时候再出手？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 600,
      "line_end": 600
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你本该等我上了床的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 604,
      "line_end": 604
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你却是个真正厉害的男人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 614,
      "line_end": 614
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一点也不错。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 616,
      "line_end": 616
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为了这件事，你已计划了很久？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 618,
      "line_end": 618
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "也有两三个月了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 620,
      "line_end": 620
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所以你就算想赖，也赖不掉的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 626,
      "line_end": 626
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你也知道我从洞房里溜掉过？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 628,
      "line_end": 628
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他微笑着，又道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 632,
      "line_end": 632
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所以我无论怎么否认，别人都一定不会相信。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 636,
      "line_end": 636
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所以你已命中注定，要做我的老婆了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 638,
      "line_end": 638
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可是……可是你为什么要做这种事呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 640,
      "line_end": 640
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为我喜欢你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 642,
      "line_end": 642
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你若真的喜欢我，就不该这样子对我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 644,
      "line_end": 644
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "就因为我真的喜欢你，所以才要这样子对付你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 646,
      "line_end": 646
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你……你难道真的要……要……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 648,
      "line_end": 648
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你……你真敢脱我衣服？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 658,
      "line_end": 658
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我不但要脱你衣服，而且还要脱光。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 660,
      "line_end": 660
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在我也已让你看过了，你还想干什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 676,
      "line_end": 676
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你真的想娶我？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 682,
      "line_end": 682
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "当然是真的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 684,
      "line_end": 684
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你……你难道看不出我已是个老太婆了！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 686,
      "line_end": 686
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我看不出，你看来简直还像是个十六七岁的小姑娘。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 688,
      "line_end": 688
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "原来真的没有男人碰过你，能娶到你这么样的女人，我真是好福气……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 700,
      "line_end": 700
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你总会有一天要后悔的，总有一天……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 704,
      "line_end": 704
    }
